    <item>
      <title>辉瑞出售 Sensodyne 制造商 Haleon 价值 30 亿英镑的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/pfizer-sells-3-billion-of-shares-in-sensodyne-maker-haleon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[辉瑞公司 (Pfizer Inc.) 出售了超过 30 亿英镑（38 亿美元）的 Haleon Plc 股票，这是这家英国消费者保健公司最大股东减持其 32% 股份的第一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/pfizer-sells-3-billion-of-shares-in-sensodyne-maker-haleon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 07:47:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿斯利康将以高达 24 亿美元的价格收购 Fusion Pharma</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/astrazeneca-to-buy-fusion-pharma-for-up-to-2-4-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿斯利康公司 (AstraZeneca Plc) 同意以高达 24 亿美元的价格收购 Fusion Pharmaceuticals Inc.，因为该公司寻求通过用更有针对性的方法取代化疗等传统方法来改变癌症治疗方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/astrazeneca-to-buy-fusion-pharma-for-up-to-2-4-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 07:17:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管日本央行加息，日本股市仍将继续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/boj-rate-hike-unlikely-to-derail-stock-rally-strategists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师表示，日本央行结束负利率政策的决定使市场基本平静，因为这一决定是提前发出的，日本股市应该能够延续近期的涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/boj-rate-hike-unlikely-to-derail-stock-rally-strategists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 04:42:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于与美国的收益率差距仍然很大，日元兑美元跌破150</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/yen-weakens-slightly-as-japan-markets-take-rate-hike-in-stride</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行结束全球最后一次负政策利率并暂时保持宽松的金融状况后，日元兑美元汇率跌破150。债券和股票双双上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/yen-weakens-slightly-as-japan-markets-take-rate-hike-in-stride</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 03:53:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
